config = errors.DEFAULT_CONFIG
p_anykey = config['p_anykey']
rand = MagicMock()
rand.random = MagicMock(side_effect=[1, p_anykey - 0.001, p_anykey + 0.001,
    0, 0])
rand.choice = MagicMock(side_effect=['q', '_', 'Z'])
assert errors.corrupt(config, 'hello', rand) == 'hql_Z'
assert errors.score(config, 'hql_Z', 'hello') == 3 * math.log(p_anykey
    ) + 2 * math.log(1 - p_anykey)
